OL,3,CLove Island's Samira Mighty says she
OL,4,Cwas overlooked after villa due to race
OL,6,FFormer Love Island star Samira Mighty
OL,7,Fhas spoken out about being the show's
OL,8,Ffirst black female contestant, saying
OL,9,Fshe felt overlooked both in the villa
OL,10,Fand after leaving the show.
OL,12,FSamira appeared on season 4 back in
OL,13,F2018 and says the lack of diversity
OL,14,Fwas clear from the start.
OL,16,F"I even asked a producer, 'Do you
OL,17,Fthink it's because I'm Black?' They
OL,18,Fwere shocked ` but it was obvious
OL,19,Fafter a few weeks. I wasn't anyone's
OL,20,Ftype," she told ITV News.
