OL,3,CLove Island's Samira Mighty says she
OL,4,Cwas overlooked after villa due to race
OL,6,FAlthough she built a loyal fan base,
OL,7,FSamira says her opportunities after
OL,8,Fthe show were far fewer than her co-
OL,9,Fstars'.
OL,11,F"When I came out of Love Island, I
OL,12,Fdefinitely should've been doing way
OL,13,Fmore ` campaigns, brand deals,
OL,14,Feverything. Why wasn't I, when I was
OL,15,Fat the same level as the other girls?"
OL,17,FDespite the challenges, Samira says
OL,18,Fshe takes pride in opening doors for
OL,19,Fothers.
