OL,3,CLove Island's Samira Mighty says she
OL,4,Cwas overlooked after villa due to race
OL,6,F"People needed someone they could look
OL,7,Fat and say, 'I look like her, I can do
OL,8,Fthat too.' And now you see islanders
OL,9,Fof all backgrounds on the show.
OL,11,F"But it's still not enough ` because
OL,12,Fit's not just about being cast, it's
OL,13,Fabout the opportunities that come
OL,14,Fafter."
OL,16,FShe also spoke about being stereotyped
OL,17,Fearly on in the villa.
OL,19,FWithin hours of arriving, she was
OL,20,Fasked if she could twerk after
OL,21,Fmentioning she was a dancer.
