OL,3,CLove Island's Samira Mighty says she
OL,4,Cwas overlooked after villa due to race
OL,6,F"I'm a West End performer, not a pole
OL,7,Fdancer. But little things like that
OL,8,Fstick," she said.
OL,10,FSince leaving Love Island, Samira has
OL,11,Fbeen building her career in both music
OL,12,Fand acting.
OL,14,FHer latest single, Cardio, is in her
OL,15,Fwords, a "sweaty party girl vibe"
OL,16,Fwritten during a heatwave in the
OL,17,Fstudio.
