OL,6,FShe's also making her big screen debut
OL,7,Fin horror film Bambi: The Reckoning,
OL,8,Fwhere she plays a character she admits
OL,9,Fmight not be too far from herself.
OL,11,F"She's a bit stuck up, a bit bougie.
OL,12,FWhen I watched it back, I was like, am
OL,13,FI playing myself?" She joked.
OL,15,FSamira says she's now determined to
OL,16,Fkeep pushing forward, teasing that she
OL,17,Fhas a "whole library" of unreleased
OL,18,Fsongs.
